The '''Warden of the Great Gate''' was the title given to the keeper of the [[Gate of Steel]], who held ultimate authority over all the [[Seven Gates]] of the [[Orfalch Echor]]. At the time of [[Tuor]]'s arrival at [[Gondolin]], this was [[Ecthelion]].<ref>{{UT|1}}, pp. 46, 50</ref>
